  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/628ef157538255fd67e5a6945d56ed64.webp?t=1619679750\" width=369 height=36 /></span><br><strong>MushrooMonster</strong> - is a first-person survival horror game.<br><br>You arrived at the forest island tonight to fight the evil mushroom monster.<br>There is only one way to kill the monster - that is to collect 12 mushrooms and burn them in a bonfire. But it will not be easy to do this, because the more mushrooms you collect, the more often the monster will attack you.<br><br>Some types of the mushrooms will help you survive:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/aa793c5f45c77ce131e6f64bdfe6370e.webp?t=1619679750\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Green mushrooms - Throw them at the monster to stop his attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/4a46018a40eaad833d6b91cb872ba25b.webp?t=1619679750\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Red mushrooms - Eat them to speed up yourself and to better see mushrooms.<br><br>But remember that the amount of these mushrooms is limited.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br>•Randomized enemy AI<br>•A lot of running and screaming<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/ebf9df0b0fd7244137e46d7bb0207b54.poster.avif?t=1619679750\" width=420 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/ebf9df0b0fd7244137e46d7bb0207b54.webm?t=1619679750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/ebf9df0b0fd7244137e46d7bb0207b54.mp4?t=1619679750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/628ef157538255fd67e5a6945d56ed64.webp?t=1619679750\" width=369 height=36 /></span><br><strong>MushrooMonster</strong> - is a first-person survival horror game.<br><br>You arrived at the forest island tonight to fight the evil mushroom monster.<br>There is only one way to kill the monster - that is to collect 12 mushrooms and burn them in a bonfire. But it will not be easy to do this, because the more mushrooms you collect, the more often the monster will attack you.<br><br>Some types of the mushrooms will help you survive:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/aa793c5f45c77ce131e6f64bdfe6370e.webp?t=1619679750\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Green mushrooms - Throw them at the monster to stop his attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/4a46018a40eaad833d6b91cb872ba25b.webp?t=1619679750\" width=32 height=32 /></span> Red mushrooms - Eat them to speed up yourself and to better see mushrooms.<br><br>But remember that the amount of these mushrooms is limited.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br>•Randomized enemy AI<br>•A lot of running and screaming<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/ebf9df0b0fd7244137e46d7bb0207b54.poster.avif?t=1619679750\" width=420 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/ebf9df0b0fd7244137e46d7bb0207b54.webm?t=1619679750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270330/extras/ebf9df0b0fd7244137e46d7bb0207b54.mp4?t=1619679750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
